<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="hero-card">
    <text class="eyebrow">REMINDER</text>
    <text class="hero-title">提醒设置</text>
    <text class="hero-sub">把提醒时间调成适合你的节奏，也可以决定是否开启默认模板课表和分享密钥。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="settings-card">
    <view class="setting-row">
      <view class="copy-block">
        <text class="setting-title">启用课程提醒</text>
        <text class="setting-desc">关闭后不会再收到课前提醒。</text>
      </view>
      <switch checked="{{remindEnabled}}" color="#c96f3b" bindchange="onToggleEnabled" />
    </view>

    <view class="setting-row stacked">
      <view class="copy-block">
        <text class="setting-title">提前提醒时间</text>
        <text class="setting-desc">选择上课前多久提醒你。</text>
      </view>
      <picker mode="selector" range="{{remindOptions}}" value="{{remindMinutesIndex}}" bindchange="onMinutesChange">
        <view class="picker-card">
          <text class="picker-value">{{remindMinutes}} 分钟</text>
          <text class="picker-arrow">></text>
        </view>
      </picker>
    </view>

    <view class="setting-row">
      <view class="copy-block">
        <text class="setting-title">周末课程也提醒</text>
        <text class="setting-desc">如果周六周日也有课，可以一起开启。</text>
      </view>
      <switch checked="{{remindWeekends}}" color="#1e3b2f" bindchange="onToggleWeekends" />
    </view>

    <view class="setting-row">
      <view class="copy-block">
        <text class="setting-title">启用默认模板课表</text>
        <text class="setting-desc">当你还没有导入自己的课表时，可以先显示默认模板。</text>
      </view>
      <switch checked="{{defaultTemplateEnabled}}" color="#c96f3b" bindchange="onToggleDefaultTemplate" />
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="preview-card">
    <text class="preview-label">CURRENT</text>
    <text class="preview-title" wx:if="{{remindEnabled}}">将在上课前 {{remindMinutes}} 分钟提醒你</text>
    <text class="preview-title" wx:else>当前已关闭课程提醒</text>
    <text class="preview-sub" wx:if="{{remindEnabled && remindWeekends}}">工作日和周末课程都会提醒。</text>
    <text class="preview-sub" wx:elif="{{remindEnabled}}">仅工作日课程参与提醒。</text>
    <text class="preview-sub" wx:else>你仍然可以随时回来重新开启。</text>
    <text class="preview-sub template-preview" wx:if="{{defaultTemplateEnabled}}">
      默认模板课表已开启，但不会覆盖你已经导入的真实课表。
    </text>
    <text class="preview-sub template-preview" wx:else>默认模板课表当前关闭。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="share-card">
    <text class="preview-label">SCHEDULE SHARE</text>
    <text class="preview-title">分享你已经导入好的课表</text>
    <text class="preview-sub">生成随机密钥后发给同学，对方在导入页输入密钥就能复制你的当前课表。</text>

    <view class="share-key-box {{shareKeyReady ? 'ready' : ''}}">
      <text class="share-key-value">{{shareKeyReady ? shareKey : '暂未生成分享密钥'}}</text>
      <text class="share-key-tip">
        {{shareKeyReady ? '重新生成后，旧密钥会立即失效。' : '登录后即可生成新的课表分享密钥。'}}
      </text>
    </view>

    <view class="share-actions">
      <view class="share-btn share-btn-primary" bindtap="onGenerateShareKey">
        {{shareKeyLoading ? '生成中...' : (shareKeyReady ? '重新生成' : '生成密钥')}}
      </view>
      <view class="share-btn share-btn-secondary" bindtap="onCopyShareKey">复制密钥</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="settings-card legal-card">
    <view class="setting-link" bindtap="goToUserAgreement">
      <view class="copy-block">
        <text class="setting-title">用户服务协议</text>
        <text class="setting-desc">查看当前版本的用户服务协议内容</text>
      </view>
      <text class="picker-arrow">></text>
    </view>

    <view class="setting-link" bindtap="goToPrivacyPolicy">
      <view class="copy-block">
        <text class="setting-title">隐私政策</text>
        <text class="setting-desc">查看我们如何收集、使用和存储用户信息</text>
      </view>
      <text class="picker-arrow">></text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <button class="save-btn" bindtap="onSave">保存设置</button>
</view>
